node.title: Reports of small plane crash near Whangamatā were false alarm
node.description: Emergency services say a report of a small plane crash near Whangamatā on the Coromandel Peninsula appears to have been a false alarm.
node.content:
["Emergency services say a report of a small plane crash near Whangamat\u0101 on the Coromandel Peninsula appears to have been a false alarm.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "A caller reported seeing a plane in trouble shortly after 10am.", "Police and ambulance helicopters were sent to Tairua Road in Hikuai, but officers now believe it was a topdressing plane working in the area."]
